snippet.title: SMBZ-G: August 2020 Update
snippet.description:
Visit https://sites.google.com/view/smbz-g for updates and the latest download link.
Join the Discord server: https://discord.com/invite/7kytgg3

Development Demo Archives: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL8aSXT9TazrDcpe5msezOjaUZZjvPnWNL

Major changes since last video:
- 00:00 New Character: Luigi / Caped Luigi.
- 00:48 Command Lists
- 00:58 Spanish Localization
- 01:44 Axem's Super Special: "Axem Cyclone"
